    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, having been curated and maintained to the most exacting standards. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous stewardship. We invite the discerning collector to experience a standard of quality that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that presents as new in every measurable aspect, offering an investment-grade driving experience.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
